snippet.title: Rush Rally 2 App Preview | iOS | AppleTV | Android
snippet.description:
Rush Rally 2 is out now on iOS, Android, tvOS and Amazon. The most authentic and thrilling rally game on your mobile device, all running at an astounding 60fps. The best rally game on mobile!

Over 72 tracks on multiple surface types!
Rally cross, Rally championship and Skill game modes. 

Console quality racing on your mobile!

http://www.rush-rally.com
